data.name: `Format: !!spam emoji <type> <length> <view?>
data.value:
- <type> represents type of spam
            - <length> represents number of characters of spam
            - <length> must be less than 1010
            - **view is optional** - doesn't allow you to copy paste well but emojis will look better
            * `!!spam emoji travel 420 view`
            * `!!spam emoji nature 8`
** ** ** **
